OL,3,CSkiers and snowboarders enjoy
OL,4,C'England's longest ski slope'
OL,6,FDozens of snow enthusiasts have
OL,7,Fbattled the wintry conditions to enjoy
OL,8,Fa day on the slopes of Weardale Ski
OL,9,FClub, something that is becoming rarer
OL,10,Fdue to climate change.
OL,12,FThe centre based on Fendrith Hill in
OL,13,FCounty Durham, claims to have the
OL,14,Flongest lift-served ski run in England.
OL,16,FThe road up to the slopes is so
OL,17,Ftreacherous that those looking to
OL,18,Faccess the club need to complete the
OL,19,Flast mile on foot.
