OL,3,CSkiers and snowboarders enjoy
OL,4,C'England's longest ski slope'
OL,6,FLocal skiers do everything they can to
OL,7,Fget to the centre when snow arrives,
OL,8,Fas those from Weardale Ski Club say
OL,9,Fhaving long periods of snow are
OL,10,Fgetting less frequent with changes in
OL,11,Fthe climate. Milder, wetter, weather
OL,12,Foften washes snow on the fells away
OL,13,Fquickly.
OL,15,FSteve Lumb from the Weardale Ski Club
OL,16,Fsaid: "They've all been watching the
OL,17,Fweather itching to get up here and
OL,18,Fwe've finally been able to open today.
OL,20,F"The skiing is fantastic and all the
OL,21,Fruns are open."
